          "dialogueType": "sendNext",
          "speaker": "NPC",
          "text": "So what happened was... I was making a new type of medicine, so I filled a pot with water and started boiling some herbs. That's when I made the mistake of... dropping the Hanging Scroll, right into the pot. Oh gosh, I pulled it out as fast as I could, but the Hanging Scroll, was already soaked and the writing on it had already disappeared.",
